HAVING
-------
- We are not allowed to use where clause after group by clause. In this case we can use having clause.

Difference Between Where and Having

WHERE                                       | HAVING
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Filters rows before grouping                | Filters rows after grouping
Cannot use aggregate functions directly     | Can use aggregate functions directly to filter groups
Cannot use derived/aliased columns in WHERE | Can use derived/aliased columns in HAVING
Can be used with SELECT, UPDATE, and DELETE | Works only with SELECT statements.
statements.

Example#1
----------
Q)Write a query to display those departments having more than 2 employees from employee table by using group by clause.
- Select department,count(*) as Total_Emp from employee2 group by department having Total_emp > 2;
                                            OR
- SELECT department, count(*) EmpCount FROM employee2 GROUP BY department HAVING EmpCount>2;

      department |  Total_Emp
      -----------------------
      HR         |  3
      IT         |  4
      Finance    |  3

Example2
-------
Q)Write a query to display those department sums of salary having more than 10000 from employee table using group by clause.
- select department,sum(salary) as total_sal from employee2 group by department having total_sal > 10000;

      department |  total_sal
      ------------------------
      HR         |  177000
      IT         |  345000
      Finance    |  225000

Example#3
---------
Q)Write a query to display sum of salary of ‘HR’ department.
- select department,sum(salary) as total_sal from employee2 group by department having department='HR';

      department |  total_sal
      ------------------------
      HR         |  177000

Note
----
- We can use HAVING without an explicit GROUP BY clause. In this case, the entire table or the result set 
  is treated as a single implicit group.

  SELECT name, salary, salary*12 ann_salary FROM employee 
  HAVING ann_salary > 900000;

